{"tid":1674671,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"星期日有追究警暴，連繫穆林集會遊行，你又知唔知？","createTime":"2019-10-25T10:40:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T15:04:45.000Z","uid":123047,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"78d9af429b235991dcca2c5a1324de003585c9fc","tid":1674671,"uid":123047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T10:40:37.000Z","msg":"代搞手岀post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有幾日就到10.27，花咗唔少心血，懇求大家分享出去🙇&zwj;♂，要有過十萬人出席✊<br />\n<br />\n海報原檔，歡迎列印<br />\n中文： <a href=\"https://t.me/SWJHK/138\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FSWJHK%2F138&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTWmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=12414154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/SWJHK/138</a><br />\n英文： <a href=\"https://t.me/SWJHK/139\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FSWJHK%2F139&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTWmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=9d196e47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/SWJHK/139</a><br />\n<br />\n反對警狂射化學毒劑<br />\n追究警暴 守護穆斯林<br />\n守護民眾 與記者同行<br />\n日期： 10月27日（周日）<br />\n時間： 3:00PM<br />\n地點： 九龍尖沙咀梳士巴利花園<br />\n主辦： <a href=\"https://t.me/SWJHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FSWJHK%2F&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTWmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=0e9bebbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/SWJHK/</a><br />\n宗旨： 透過集會聚焦有關訴求，引起全球穆斯林及民眾關注<br />\n當日絕對和平，嚴防政府陰招， 自製暴力衝突搶走傳媒焦點<br />\n(如有改動，請以最新公佈為準)<br />\n<br />\n重要！顏色水根本不是水！<br />\n是化學毒劑，令皮膚很灼熱刺痛！<br />\n不要被政府誤導，不要叫顏色水！<br />\n我們必須正名，請大家以後叫「化學毒劑」(poisonous chemical agents, or poisonous chemicals)及「化武車」(chemical weapon vehicles)。<br />\n<br />\n📣誠徵大量義工<br />\n▪️做糾察<br />\n▪️周圍宣傳10.27<br />\n▪️吹雞叫人去10.27<br />\n▪️派傳單，貼連儂牆<br />\n歡迎聯繫 @HKgerGoGoGoal<br />\n仲有其他工作，詳情： <a href=\"https://t.me/SWJHK/117\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FSWJHK%2F117&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTWmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=7adfd812\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/SWJHK/117</a><br />\n<br />\n#宣傳品<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/571nCnM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F571nCnM.jpg&h=de5b838a&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/25/183932_0556083ee3677d604f9f25fba1892eac.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F25%2F183932_0556083ee3677d604f9f25fba1892eac.jpeg&h=67d73351&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pWXuhnQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpWXuhnQ.jpg&h=b137091d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e3a34943297acf61660b958f9d33454a86bd217","tid":1674671,"uid":123047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T10:41:30.000Z","msg":"自推1/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e891fef59e1d492e51d66e0069ab55dbc4ef6a6d","tid":1674671,"uid":122711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T10:41:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2df5ce8058ed6b59e3441781fb38a7b4c0f6c0e4","tid":1674671,"uid":123047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T10:41:50.000Z","msg":"自推2/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e5e4992c324147a8be55b6b077f126ce0a06c8","tid":1674671,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T10:41:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af67fc9c0d04e2b3fcccff09082bdb0aa510ebf7","tid":1674671,"uid":331346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T10:42:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d32ddb6214929211b38d26e45ac96695b8abc9b","tid":1674671,"uid":123047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T10:42:29.000Z","msg":"自推3/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d4dd9be1e64271207a1ff27caa7cee0052e0e25","tid":1674671,"uid":6